description:
This is a 30 minute workout called '30 MIN BEGINNER RUN INTERVALS | Treadmill Follow Along! #ibxrunning' from the channel IBX Running.
The workout falls under Cardio/Treadmill and Cardio/Running.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Treadmill for this workout.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Progression Quest vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Today we have the perfect run workout for beginners! Milder speeds and short intervals! Let's do it!

30 minutes of run and recovery intervals

All speeds and inclines are suggestions. Please stay safe and within your comfort zone!
